Vision: A place where someone can go unwind and get away. The website will be interactive and its content captivating. Pictures and videos capturing natures most natural moments.
The author is able to change the theme of the entire site and also the theme of each individual post. This allows for fine-tuned communication. Viewers can choose whether media is creative, insightfl, bueatiflul, or blah. This allows the author some feedback. The feedback is used to make decisions on future posts and themes.  
Content targets is 8-inf years olds looking for a creative bite during thir free time. Viewers are left with thier curiosity heightened and mood brightened. 
